Until the build system (eventually cmake) creates the following links, please do so by hand.

cd SCIRun/dbg/pysci
ln -s ../lib/libpysci.so _pysci.so
ln -s ../../src/pysci/pysci.py pysci.py



You must set the following env var to the location of your builds on-the-fly-libs dir

SCIRUN_ON_THE_FLY_LIBS_DIR=<full path to your SCIRun/dbg/on-the-fly-libs/>

You must set your PYTHONPATH env var to your builds pysci dir

PYTHONPATH=<full path to your SCIRun/dbg/pysci/>